{"word":"G4531 - σαλεύω - saleúō - sal-yoo'-o - Move","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">σαλεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">saleúō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">sal-yoo'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Move</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - அசை, குலுங்கு, கிளப்பு, சஞ்சலப்படு"},{"paragraph":"to agitate, shake"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4535 - σάλος - sálos - sal'-os/4535\">G4535</a>; to <i>waver</i>, that is, <i>agitate</i>, <i>rock</i>, <i>topple</i> or (by implication) <i>destroy</i>; figuratively to <i>disturb</i>, <i>incite:</i> - move, shake (together), which can [-not] be shaken, stir up.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4531/4531\">G4531</a>, <a href=\"#/G4535/4535\">G4535</a>"}]}